l adds quick (they die fast and once dead stop sucking down mana), send all damage to wars (big HP max's out CH), and twitch/rod/ft the clerics. There are a plethora of other tactics, but they all go towards supporting one of those strategies. <p>Mosushi, Lizard Master of the Fish<br><i>"I will gladly pay you Tuesday for Sushi today!"</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukzanverto.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kzan Verto</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Giver of da juice (tm)</span><br>  Posts: 904<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/7/02 2:41:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2493.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mana Cap</span><hr size=1> Thanks to Wither and Viren for the help on this.<br><br>Base mana = level ((starting int/5)+2)<br>Direct mana = sum of all + mana items<br><br>Indirect mana for:<br><br>int up to 200= level/5 * (sum of + int items up to 200)<br>int greater than 200 = level/10 * (sum of + int items over 200)<br> <p>Kzan Verto<BR>Giver of "da juice" (tm)<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=220314" target="new">My Magelo Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umistressoftherose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mistress of the Rose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Black Rose</span><br>  Posts: 379<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/8/02 7:05:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2493.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> Hey Fuvi I was told by someone (can't remember offhand) that the flowing thought 2 from Zephy